# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
@angular/compiler
@angular/router

### Is this a regression?
No

### Description
Ngcc does not append the inputs which suit with the directive selector. 

## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction
https://github.com/thesayyn/ivy-repro


## Current behavior 
Ngcc generates directive def like so
```typescript
RouterLink.ngDirectiveDef = …µngcc0.…µdefineDirective({
    ...
    inputs: {
      // Expected routerLink input
        queryParams: 'queryParams',
        fragment: 'fragment',
        queryParamsHandling: 'queryParamsHandling',
        preserveFragment: 'preserveFragment',
        skipLocationChange: 'skipLocationChange',
        replaceUrl: 'replaceUrl',
        state: 'state'
    }
});
```

## Expected behavior
```typescript
RouterLink.ngDirectiveDef = …µngcc0.…µdefineDirective({
    ...
    inputs: {
        routerLink: 'routerLink',
        queryParams: 'queryParams',
        fragment: 'fragment',
        queryParamsHandling: 'queryParamsHandling',
        preserveFragment: 'preserveFragment',
        skipLocationChange: 'skipLocationChange',
        replaceUrl: 'replaceUrl',
        state: 'state'
    }
});
```

